Row.entry:
In cohort A, imaging-based PFS was significantly longer in
the olaparib group than in the control group (median, 7.4 mo vs. 3.6 mo;
HR for progression or death, 0.34; 95% CI, 0.25–0.47;
P < .001). The median OS in cohort A was 18.5 mo in the olaparib group and 15.1 mo in the control group; 81% of the patients in the control group who had disease progression
crossed over to receive olaparib
